  <brief_title>Near Infrared Spectroscopy (NIRS)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Validation of Near Infrared Spectroscopy (NIRS) Neuro-monitoring During Deep Hypothermic Circulatory Arrest for Aortic Arch Surgery</official_title>
  <sponsors>
