  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is designed to assess the feasibility of evaluating cerebral saturation during
      critical periods of deep hypothermia circulatory arrest and Selective Antegrade Cerebral
      Perfusion.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
